data.description: Welcome to Tranquility. This 3 Bed 2 Bath Doublewide Home offers a Split Floor Plan, Vaulted Ceilings, and Lots of Natural Light for a Spacious Feel as soon as You Step through the Front Door. This Home also Boasts a Metal Roof, Wood Siding, and Plenty of Storage. The Extended Deck provides the Perfect place to Enjoy Your Morning Coffee, watch the Wildlife that Roam the Area, or Gaze up at the Stars and Immerse Yourself in the Picturesque Surroundings and Crisp Mountain Air. Located in a Tight-knit Community Close to Hiking Trails and many other Outdoor Recreational Activities You'll love Living in Overgaard. Whether You're looking for a Permanent Home or a Mountain Retreat Nestled in the Tall Pines Your New Home Awaits.  Call today or stop by!
